model.mediator

Class ModelManagerServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.mediator.ModelManagerServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelServer

    public class ModelManagerServer
extends java.lang.Object
implements ModelServer
    ModelManagerServer implementation. The class is responsable for modifing the server's data and return delivarables to high-level entities (RMI SERVER) in the completion of a certain process in the system.
    Version:
    1.5
    Author:
    Group 4
